OL,5, A mum has said she will be forced to   
OL,6, watch her baby daughter die if certain 
OL,7, cystic fibrosis medicines are axed.    
OL,9,FThe National Institute for Health and  
OL,10,FCare Excellence (NICE) has withdrawn   
OL,11,Fits recommendation for a number cystic 
OL,12,Ffibrosis (CF) medicines due to cost.   
OL,14,FCharlotte Perkins, 38, whose           
OL,15,F17-month-old daughter Delilah has had  
OL,16,FCF since birth, said she was           
OL,17,F"devastated".                          
OL,19,FNICE said it is evaluating the "cost   
OL,20,Feffectiveness" of the medicines so that
OL,21,F"taxpayers continue to get value".     
